sequenceDiagram
    actor U as 用户
    participant W as WebUI
    participant API as AINRF API
    participant TH as Task Harness
    participant P as Prompt Composer
    participant L as Launcher
    participant E as 执行环境<br/>(本地/SSH)
    participant DB as SQLite

    U->>W: 选择 Workspace + Environment<br/>输入任务描述
    W->>API: POST /tasks
    API->>TH: 创建任务
    TH->>P: compose_task_prompt()
    Note over P: 五层组合：<br/>global → workspace →<br/>environment → profile →<br/>task input
    P-->>TH: rendered_prompt
    TH->>L: build_launcher()
    L->>E: 启动 Claude Code
    activate E
    E-->>L: stdout/stderr 流
    L-->>TH: 实时输出
    TH-->>API: SSE 流
    API-->>W: 实时显示
    TH->>DB: 持久化输出
    deactivate E
    E-->>L: 进程结束
    L-->>TH: exit code
    TH-->>API: 状态更新<br/>succeeded / failed
    API-->>W: 任务完成
    U->>W: 点击回放
    W->>API: GET /tasks/{id}/replay
    API->>DB: 读取历史输出
    DB-->>API: 完整输出
    API-->>W: 回放展示
